FT  29 JUN 93 / Commodities and Agriculture: Bolivian oil plan agreed
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By DEBORAH HARGREAVES
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
PAN ANDEAN Resources, the oil and gas exploration company, has agreed a
joint venture with Australia's BHP to explore for oil in central Bolivia.
BHP will finance a Dollars 6m seismic programme to gather geological
information on the area.
Pan Andean was set up in 1988 to exploit resource opportunities in South
America's the Andean region.
