   NEW YORK
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
THE United Nations Security Council yesterday expressed concern at recent
criticism by Iraq of the work of a UN commission which demarcated the
Kuwait-Iraq border, Reuter reports from New York. The Council warned Baghdad
